column2: select ar.name, ar.artistid, sum(il.quantity*il.unitprice) as totalPrice, count(il.invoicelineid) as num from chinook.artist ar   join chinook.album al on al.artistId=ar.artistId   join chinook.track tr on tr.albumId=al.albumid   join  chinook.invoiceline il on il.trackid=tr.trackid group by ar.name, ar.artistid   order by # desc,#,#
